9
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:23,020
Uh-oh.

10
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:24,160
You pick it up.

11
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:29,720
The screen brightness totally hits your eyes, and you see a text message from a friend.

12
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,560
Or, you know, maybe a partner.

13
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:33,140
The stakes are getting higher.

14
00:00:33,340 --> 00:00:33,760
Exactly.

15
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:39,520
