16
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:42,160
Something that required some actual coordination.

17
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:42,780
Right.

18
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,300
Maybe a little bit of compromise.

19
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:48,520
