38
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:28,880
Fine.

39
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:29,700
Yes.

40
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:38,980
Or, worst of all, is it that dreaded, passive-aggressive fine that actually means the exact, literal

41
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,420
